## вңЁ Features Implemented

### Core Stack
| Technology | Version | Status |
|------------|---------|--------|
| Electron | 33.x | вң… |
| React | 18.x | вң… |
| TypeScript | 5.x | вң… |
| TailwindCSS | 4.x | вң… |
| Vite | 6.x | вң… |

### Features

#### рҹӘҹ Custom Titlebar
- Frameless window with custom controls
- Minimize, maximize, close buttons
- Drag region for window movement
- Theme toggle in titlebar

#### рҹҺЁ Theme System (Light/Dark)
- Light theme (default) and dark theme
- CSS variables for easy customization
- Toggle via:
  - UI button in titlebar
  - Toggle switch in Theme Settings
  - Keyboard shortcut: `вҢҳ+Shift+T` / `Ctrl+Shift+T`
  - Menu: View вҶ’ Toggle Theme

#### рҹ”Ң IPC Communication Examples
- Get system information (platform, memory, CPU, versions)
- Show native dialogs (message, file open, file save)
- File read/write operations
- Shell operations (open URL, show in folder)
- Type-safe API via contextBridge

#### рҹ“Ӣ Context Menu Examples
- Custom action menus (right-click)
- Text editing menu (cut, copy, paste)
- Dynamic menu with separators
- Action logging

#### рҹ”„ Auto-Updater
- [electron-updater](file:///Users/jeegargoyani/jigoLearn/electron-template-by-jigo/src/main/updater.ts) integration
- GitHub releases provider configured
- IPC channels for update status
- Programmatic update control

#### рҹ“Ұ Build & Packaging
- [electron-builder.yml](file:///Users/jeegargoyani/jigoLearn/electron-template-by-jigo/electron-builder.yml) configuration
- macOS: DMG installer
- Windows: NSIS installer
- Linux: AppImage, deb, rpm

