## рҹҡҖ How to Use

### Quick Start

```bash
# Navigate to project
cd electron-template-by-jigo

# Install dependencies
npm install

# Start development (with HMR)
npm run dev

# Build and run production
npm run preview

# Package for distribution
npm run package
```

### Available Scripts

| Command | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| `npm run dev` | Start dev server with HMR |
| `npm run build` | Build all for production |
| `npm run preview` | Build and run production |
| `npm run package` | Package for current OS |
| `npm run package:mac` | Package for macOS |
| `npm run package:win` | Package for Windows |
| `npm run package:linux` | Package for Linux |

