## рҹҺҜ Next Steps

1. **Customize the template** for your specific application
2. **Replace the placeholder icon** with your app icon
3. **Update package.json** with your app details
4. **Configure auto-updater** with your GitHub repository
5. **Add your React components** to the renderer

The template is ready to use as a starting point for any Electron desktop application!
